Note from TieDyeSheep:

Q:Why are you using a scheduler instead of coloring the sheep in the OnCreatureSpawn event?

A:The sheep color is apparently being overwritten between the event and when they appear in the world. See the following links for details.

http://leaky.bukkit.org/issues/606

http://forums.bukkit.org/threads/solved-oncreaturespawn-and-making-colored-sheep.10280/